OL,3,CUK to miss out on #600m in tax due to
OL,4,CUS exemption, says HMRC
OL,6,FThe UK is set to miss out on around
OL,7,F#600 million in tax each year
OL,8,Ffollowing a deal allowing the US to be
OL,9,Fexempt from a global tax commitment,
OL,10,Faccording to HMRC figures.
OL,12,FIt confirmed the expected tax
OL,13,Freduction as part of scrutiny by
OL,14,FParliament's Public Accounts Committee
OL,15,F(PAC) into tax paid by major
OL,16,Fmultinational firms in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
