OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1783646288
OL,3,CUK to miss out on #600m in tax due to
OL,4,CUS exemption, says HMRC
OL,6,FThe committee warned the UK tax
OL,7,Fauthority must better tackle the large
OL,8,Frisk of global firms diverting their
OL,9,Fprofits overseas and therefore
OL,10,Fshifting tax jurisdictions.
OL,12,FThe PAC found HMRC's approach to
OL,13,Fcollecting tax from large businesses
OL,14,Fis "generally working well".
OL,16,FHowever, it said there are still
OL,17,F"significantly high" risks related to
OL,18,Fmultinationals potentially diverting
OL,19,Fprofits across borders.
OL,26,@vD@DOUvD@[O]yD@AOUyD@TO]
