OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1783646288
OL,3,CUK to miss out on #600m in tax due to
OL,4,CUS exemption, says HMRC
OL,6,FOf the #70.1 billion of tax under
OL,7,Fconsideration in 2025 as part of
OL,8,Finvestigations into large businesses,
OL,9,FHMRC estimates around #21 billion of
OL,10,Fthis faces international risks.
OL,12,FThe committee is therefore calling on
OL,13,Fthe tax body to provide further
OL,14,Finsights on the risks involved and how
OL,15,Fit can better tackle potential issues.
OL,17,FIt comes after a landmark
OL,18,Finternational tax rate was agreed in
OL,19,FJanuary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
