OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1783646288
OL,3,CUK to miss out on #600m in tax due to
OL,4,CUS exemption, says HMRC
OL,6,FThe deal saw nearly 150 countries
OL,7,Fagree to a 15% global minimum tax to
OL,8,Fstop large global companies shifting
OL,9,Fprofits to jurisdictions with lower
OL,10,Ftaxes.
OL,12,FHowever, the US will be exempt from
OL,13,Fthe deal, with was finalised by the
OL,14,FOrganisation for Economic Cooperation
OL,15,Fand Development.
OL,17,FNicole Newbury, director of large
OL,18,Fbusiness compliance at HMRC, told the
OL,19,Fcommittee the US exemption from the
OL,20,FPillar 2 tax rule will have an impact
OL,21,Fon the UK's tax income.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
