PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1783646288
OL,3,CUK to miss out on #600m in tax due to
OL,4,CUS exemption, says HMRC
OL,6,FShe said: "It has reduced the benefit
OL,7,F` the additional tax that will be paid
OL,8,Fin the UK ` by about #600 million a
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,F"The forecast for what Pillar 2 will
OL,12,Fbring into the UK has now reduced to
OL,13,F#1.6 billion a year, so there will be
OL,14,Fa monetary impact."
OL,16,FClive Betts MP, deputy chairman of the
OL,17,Fcommittee, said: "The UK still risks
OL,18,Fbleeding a significant amount of its
OL,19,Ftax take overseas through the cross-
OL,20,Fborder diversion of multinationals'
OL,21,Fprofits over borders.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUvD@SO]yD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
