CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1783646288
OL,3,CUK to miss out on #600m in tax due to
OL,4,CUS exemption, says HMRC
OL,6,F"HMRC should be bearing down on work
OL,7,Fto understand how companies are
OL,8,Fcomplying with new rules on
OL,9,Finternational minimum rates for
OL,10,Fcorporation tax, particularly in light
OL,11,Fof the parallel agreement with the US
OL,12,Fexempting their own companies from
OL,13,Fthese rules."
OL,15,FAn HRMC spokeswoman said: "The UK
OL,16,Fcontinues to lead the way
OL,17,Finternationally in making sure that
OL,18,Fmultinational businesses pay the tax
OL,19,Fthat's legally due.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@MO]wD@[OU
